{"tid":874892,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打一齊組團扮睇樓壓價嚇下班業主!","createTime":"2018-10-24T13:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T01:07:18.000Z","uid":54870,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"16f411a6da9caba1cc784916e3fb5441d966622d","tid":874892,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6030229&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DFN%26message%3D6030229%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=8%2BDi7b%2FJEqCVOJLQR6yxE9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6ed40993\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6030229&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n買賣, 都係捉心理既姐。 <br />\n巴打不如一齊組團去睇樓, 就算唔打算買或者根本無錢買, 都可以扮睇樓, 之後就同業主講減30% 即七折, 如果唔係就唔買。業主一定唔會肯。 <br />\n但如果不斷有唔同人去睇樓, 都係一樣不斷壓佢價, 就會對業主做成好大既心理壓力。 <br />\n當大部分既業主經過不斷壓價而做成信心崩潰, 樓價就會突然瀑瀉。 <br />\n<br />\n而家欠既就係點火既藥引, 一爆就不可收拾。"},{"pid":"1b4b2805e205ad4b72c3a161d8b8e6336d76439e","tid":874892,"uid":202122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"有趣有趣"},{"pid":"5e668f25a059a3c3da0e8a3a43105a9187cc534b","tid":874892,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f411a6da9caba1cc784916e3fb5441d966622d","tid":874892,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6030229&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DFN%26message%3D6030229%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=8%2BDi7b%2FJEqCVOJLQR6yxE9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6ed40993\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN